---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CTABand from '@/components/CTABand.astro';

const investmentPlans = [
  'Retirement Savings Plans (RSP)',
  'Registered Education Savings Plans (RESP)',
  'Tax Free Savings Accounts (TFSA)',
  'Registered Disability Savings Plans (RDSP)',
  'Corporate Savings',
  'Individual Pension Plans',
  'Group Pension Plans',
  'Group Retirement Savings Plans',
  'Mutual Funds and Segregated Funds',
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Investments | Heidi Blondin Financial"
  description="Heidi Blondin is a Financial Advisor offering personalized investment planning including RSP, RESP, TFSA, RDSP, and more for clients across Ontario."
>

  <section class="bg-brand-plum py-20">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-display text-white text-balance" style="font-optical-sizing: auto;">Investments</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <div class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>Canadians that work with a Financial Advisor tend to be more disciplined with their savings, have more confidence about their financial future, and accumulate more assets. So given these trends, why are so many people trying to go it alone?</p>
        <p>When it comes to investing, a Financial Advisor can help you establish a budget, prepare for the unexpected, set realistic goals and strategies, and help you make educated decisions about your money. This increases your chances of financial success. The only thing you need to get started is a commitment to your financial future.</p>
        <p>Heidi Blondin is a Financial Advisor that thoroughly enjoys the process of establishing goals and developing strategies to achieve them. She provides personalized service to help clients fine tune their monthly budget to better address their goals and priorities.</p>
        <p>Heidi offers a broad range of investment plans including:</p>
      </div>

      <ul class="mt-4 font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed space-y-1.5">
        {investmentPlans.map(plan => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-brand-gold mt-0.5">→</span>
            <span>{plan}</span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTABand heading="Contact Heidi Today" />

  <section class="bg-brand-tintPlum section-gap">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl">
      <div class="bg-white p-8 border-l-4 border-brand-gold">
        <blockquote class="font-sans text-[17px] text-brand-ink/75 leading-relaxed italic">
          "Heidi has been my trusted advisor and friend for several years. She and her team have provided sound financial guidance in the investment of my life savings. I am able to sleep at night knowing that they are invested according to my risk comfort levels. I also reap the rewards of various solutions that provide the most tax efficient income in my retirement. I would encourage anyone looking for a great Financial Advisor to call Heidi. T.O. – Kingston, Ontario"
        </blockquote>
        <p class="mt-6 font-sans text-[14px] text-brand-plum font-medium">
          <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=Heidi+Blondin+Financial" class="hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors underline">Write A Review For Heidi On Google+</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
